<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>typeof和instanceof操作符在JavaScript中的用法和区别</title>

    <style>
      body {
        font-family:
          -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
